  "title": "Site Engineer [Building]/ New D&B proj/ 5day/Upto $7K+VB/A1 Maincon MNC/ West",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Up to $7,000 basic + Variable bonus.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Permanent position/ 5 work days</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Participate in the construction new design and building project at Jurong east area.</strong></p></li></ul><p> <strong>Our client is a reputable MNC and leading A1 main contractors diverse in civil and large-scale infrastructure projects</strong>.</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Report to the Project Manager</p></li><li><p>Support project and construction management for building projects</p></li><li><p>Develop and review architectural and engineering drawings to ensure compliance with specifications and regulations</p></li><li><p>Liaise with architects, engineers, and other technical teams to ensure design requirements are met</p></li><li><p>Oversee construction activities, including planning, implementation, and monitoring of work schedules in accordance with the master and detailed work programme</p></li><li><p>Liaise with consultants on technical issues and coordinate with subcontractors on site activities</p></li><li><p>Prepare reports and method statements</p></li><li><p>Monitor ongoing construction activities</p></li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bachelor’s Degree in Civil Engineering or Building</p></li><li><p>Experience in large-scale building construction projects preferred</p><p><strong>Other Information:</strong><br /><strong>To apply please click on the APPLY NOW button or email your resume to </strong><a href=\"mailto:search84@searchindex.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">search84@searchindex.com.sg</a><strong> with the following details inside your resume </strong><br /><strong>• Reason for leaving each past & current employment</strong><br /><strong>• Salary drawn for each past & current employment</strong><br /><strong>• Expected Salary</strong><br /><strong>• Earliest availability date</strong><br /><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.  </strong><br /><strong>Lionel Cheow</strong><br /><strong>EA License | 14C7092</strong><br /><strong>EA Registration Number | R1105005</strong></p></li></ul>",
